events.name: San Francisco 49ers at Los Angeles Rams

headlines.description: — Everything seemed to indicate the San Francisco 49ers were in for a long night when they traveled south on a short week without Brock Purdy, Nick Bosa, George Kittle and their top three wide receivers to face the surging Los Angeles Rams.
headlines.shortLinkText: Short-handed 49ers stop Rams on downs in overtime, preserving a 26-23 victory
